## 👤 User Stories
* **As a Growth PM**, I want to filter out "Burst Bot" activity so that my funnel optimization experiments are based on real human intent.
* **As a Marketing Lead**, I want to identify "Champions" so that I can reward them with loyalty incentives to protect the $970k revenue stream.
* **As a Data-Informed PM**, I want to see exactly where the 12.9% drop-off occurs to prioritize checkout UI/UX improvements.

